code: import axios from'axios';export const createOrUpdateUser=async(userDetails,idToken)=>{return await axios.post("".concat(process.env.REACT_APP_API,"/createOrUpdateUser"),{userDetails},{headers:{idToken}});};export const checkUser=async email=>{return await axios.post("".concat(process.env.REACT_APP_API,"/checkUserRole"),{email});};export const currentUser=async(email,idToken)=>{return await axios.post("".concat(process.env.REACT_APP_API,"/getCurrentUser"),{email},{headers:{idToken}});};export const getUsers=async idToken=>{return await axios.get("".concat(process.env.REACT_APP_API,"/getUsers"),{headers:{idToken}});};
